{"tid":1719251,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急警告：藍絲將全面進場打手足 戰爭開始","createTime":"2019-11-14T05:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T07:16:11.000Z","uid":13936,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"61f8ec8df40f86c9c31dad8d7c47c6441811f17d","tid":1719251,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"手足要小心<br />\n已經有手足被打 <br />\n夜晚落單隨時被殺"},{"pid":"b3f62f55865c7063e0f926d7b2dd23bb4976cffd","tid":1719251,"uid":13936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:04:54.000Z","msg":"長期置頂"},{"pid":"73da932c8c92ca96b8e935148a0f7924eb083593","tid":1719251,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7d3ab9f30fe633cd8705be37278b4fbeaaba8d0","tid":1719251,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"585e84d92939b56eaded2e6142bb656965ef46a9","tid":1719251,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"htt